title: Airdropped Nudes, Affion Crockett, New Music & More
itunes:title: Airdropped Nudes, Affion Crockett, New Music & More
description:
Today on The Breakfast Club we are joined by Affion Crockett who shows off his VERY impressive impressions and talks about the new age of comedy we live in. Later on we have our listeners call in and discuss if they have ever had nudes airdropped to them. Donkey of The Day goes to a perverted plane passenger. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
